its not like im trying to only defend brad..because i know how rude and evil he can get..but its just little stupid things that other people do to make him feel like shit when he disagrees with them one time..i know i would get pissed off and flip out to if everyone called me fucking stupid and that i didnt know what i was talking about if i put my two sense in something like so small..and when people make him feel like shit..they are definetly going to get a shit storm thrown back at their faces which only causes more shit..doesnt make sense to me..but owell.. hmmm friends are really pissing me off anymore..its like i dont know what the fuck they are doing, and when i try to give them my advice that they OH SO NEED..i get bitched at because they dont like the cold hard truth that they need to be hearing..maybe if i start being truthful and say whats really on my mind instead of trying to be nice about it so that no one getts hurt to everyone that they would get the picture.. okay..enough of that..im bored hopefully everything goes well at sheenas party tomorrow
